data.description: LOWEST PRICED PROPERTY IN MILANO! This BRIGHT and SPACIOUS condo features an open floor concept on the main floor along with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths. Situated on one of the BEST LOTS in the community overlooking the widest part of the lake. The master bedroom has high vaulted ceilings, walk in closet and an on-suite bathroom with walk in shower and dual sinks. This home includes a newer A/C unit in (Dec. '21) and newer roof (Aug. '19). Ideally located in North Naples within A+ rated school district. Milano's amenities include lighted tennis courts, community pool, basketball court and dog park. All located just minutes from I-75 and close to many shopping and dining options and 10 minutes to beaches!
